      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OUR FRANKIE GIRL (8) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (30.03) in a Grade 5 at Gosford. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Ready to return to form. FLY AROUND (6) clocked a decent 18.26 when placed over 320m at this track last start in a Grade 5. Expected to feature again. SILENT MINUTE (7) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 18.35 beating Fantasia Queen. Leading player again. KAROLINE BANNER (4) showed plenty of dash to record a last start win. Hard to beat again.",
